Package dataDriver

Class FileIO

java.lang.Object
dataDriver.FileIO
All Implemented Interfaces:
InterfaceCsvDelimiter
public class FileIO extends Object implements InterfaceCsvDelimiter
Driver that handles all file I/O operations on CSV files. This object can perform basic CRUD opertations, and remove duplicates in CSV files.
